  "name": "Deploy - Translator HQ Connector (for Bigcommerce, Woocommerce etc)",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-translator-hq-connector-for-bigcommerce-woocommerce-etc\">Deploy - Translator HQ Connector (for Bigcommerce, Woocommerce etc)</h1>\n<p><span><span>T</span></span><span><span>his article explains how to deploy the integration for a Translator HQ Connector once a signed solutions agreement has been received along with payment (1st installment of payment plan or full amount):</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Enabling the Web Service</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (62).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgsEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to clients Retail Express</p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>Quick Links &gt; Web Services Configuration</strong></p>\n<p>3. Set <strong>WebStoreV2</strong> to enabled</p>\n<p>4. Click <strong>Save Changes</strong></p>\n<p>  </p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (63).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powgxEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Select the macro <strong>Translator HQ &gt; Translator HQ Connector deployment</strong></p>\n<p>3. Enter the clients name in the ticket</p>\n<p>4. Enter the clients retailexpress database name in the ticket</p>\n<p>5. Enter the clients email address in the ticket</p>\n<p>6. Enter the date the signed solutions agreement was signed in the ticket</p>\n<p>7. Select the appropriate ecommerce platform name from the list (e.g. Woo Commerce, Big Commerce) and remove the others from the ticket</p>\n<p>8. Submit the ticket as <strong>Open </strong>(it will then appear in unassigned and be passed to a customer service team member to deal with from there)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
